        "title": "Eclipse code template based on highlight",
        "body": "<p>In the Eclipse platform, I want to create java custom code template based on a highlighted field name. for example, I highlight a field name, \"name\", right click and then insert a code template base on the \"name\". what is the variable name for the highlighted field ?<\/p>\n\n<p>Thanks. <\/p>\n",
