        "creation_date": 1467212539,
        "body": "<p>Code Templates as configured in the Preferences in 'Java > Code Style > Code Templates' don't support this.<\/p>\n\n<p>For editor templates as configured in 'Java > Editor > Templates' <code>${word_selection}<\/code> is possibly what you want.<\/p>\n",
